snippet.title: Arcade ZX Collection: BOTANIC
snippet.description:
This is my 3th game for the Zx Spectrum 48K, totally homebrew, using for programming Notepad++ in pure assembler
Now you can purchase it : 4€ digital version, 10€ tape version
Email me: bubu.marcianito@gmail.com
